  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high, then add the <strong>skewers</strong> to a bowl of <strong>cold water</strong> and set aside</p>\n<p>De-seed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>,<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>cut into wedges then add them to a <strong>tin foil </strong>lined baking tray and drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> </p>\n<p>Put the tray under the grill for 10 min or until softened and lightly charred, then once done, transfer the <strong>roasted pepper</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> and reserve the tray</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the red pepper is cooking, add the <strong>lamb mince</strong>, <strong>baharat</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a large mixing bowl and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p>\n<p>Divide the <strong>lamb mixture</strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> and shape into <strong>sausage shapes</strong> – these are your<strong> lamb kebabs</strong></p>\n<p>Skewer each <strong>lamb kebab</strong> and set aside</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, cook for 7-8 min or until tender with a bite</p>\n<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lamb kebabs</strong> to the reserved baking tray (use<strong> tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p>\n<p>Put the tray under the grill for 10 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!), turning once half way – these are your <strong>baharat lamb kebabs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>\n<p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> to the <strong>food processor</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></span>, 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>salt</strong> and the<strong> juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong></p>\n<p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>red pepper hummus</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2112.-step-5-x400.jpg",
